title: This is the Craziest Wingsuit Flight I Have Ever Seen
content:
Extreme sports athlete Graham Dickinson recently shared footage of his insane flight through the ‘Rock Star Line’ in Chamonix, France. Dickinson was tailed by his wingman and filming partner Dario. 
 
The two reached speeds in excess of 180 km/h. Check out the helmet cam footage below from Graham’s flight. Absolutely bonkers.
